{"type": "article", "id": 25925, "title": "宠物小床", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-25T06:59:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 78, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702142119jYHxEzOdsbJFoapt.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这个名叫 Dog Den 的宠物小床是 <a href=\"http://razy2.com/\" onclick=\"__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'outbound-article', 'http://razy2.com/', 'Razy2 Design Group');\" target=\"_blank\">Razy2 Design Group</a> 为波兰家具装饰品牌 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mnomodesign/\" onclick=\"__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'outbound-article', 'https://www.facebook.com/mnomodesign/', 'Mnomo');\" target=\"_blank\">Mnomo</a> 所设计的产品。Dog Den 的床架为橡木制，床垫使用了杜邦面料（Cordura），不会吸收液体或者气味，非常适合宠物犬使用。小床整体设计新颖，放在家中也能很好地融入环境，不会显得突兀。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142117GD1V6pSQCbmzc7Lr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142118u4bjGKkpoe31JwUt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142118Kvj0B6ysTAoDpcLG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}